{"tid":1976771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★口罩假證書橫行全球 真偽連廠商都難以辨別","createTime":"2020-04-17T12:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T15:27:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d728db653879a6f1818f46473523143c301e1ec","tid":1976771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7ieRre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7ieRre.jpg&h=b54f31b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐盟CE認證是產品信心保證，除把口罩出口到歐洲必須取得歐盟CE認證，不少香港藥房都以此招徠客人購買口罩。然而，證書真偽卻連口罩廠商都難以辨別。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>內地公司冒稱可作歐盟驗證資格</strong><br />\n<br />\n記者於內地網頁找到多個聲稱可以提供口罩歐盟認證服務的公司，有公司以低價及快速驗證推銷，但實際上並無相關歐盟驗證資格。記者以口罩貿易商身份，以微信聯絡到兩名深圳中介，表示手上有批口罩想出口到外國，希望辦好歐盟CE認證。<br />\n<br />\n有一名女中介聲稱可於兩周內辦好CE認證，價格為1.8萬元人民幣，惟她提供的證書樣本，經查證後卻非正規的CE證書。記者問有關證書是否能確保口罩可供出口到歐洲，對方竟表示：「不能保證100%哦！」相比之下，另一間正規的中介公司就表示需時五周才辦到CE認證，價格為13.6萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>無良商人以偽證書騙消費者</strong><br />\n<br />\n由於現時各國都對口罩需求殷切，因此一時之間口罩貿易十分興旺，不少廠家為求通關，以及令買家有信心，都會想盡辦法取得認證證書。不少無良商人借機偽造口罩證書，售予廠商；同時，部份不良廠商亦魚目混珠，以偽造口罩證書吸引買家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/460972/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%86%92%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E8%BE%A6%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89-%E5%81%87%E8%AD%89%E6%9B%B8%E4%BD%A0%E9%81%87%E9%81%8E%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%259F%25A5%2F460972%2F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%2586%2592%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E5%2581%2587%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%259B%25B8%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E9%2581%2587%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25B0%2591&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU91SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=a71c597c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/460972/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%86%92%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E8%BE%A6%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89-%E5%81%87%E8%AD%89%E6%9B%B8%E4%BD%A0%E9%81%87%E9%81%8E%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91</a>"},{"pid":"5a0033f0ed54a968b8e404d31f82343874ce1cf0","tid":1976771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff345f529ef6db859b458a5eb4c57fdb64134309","tid":1976771,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"真偽連廠商都難 一文睇清真假<br />\n01記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f212f3df8607910b0fdaf879b01a33dc7675b952","tid":1976771,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"你點辨的"}]}